  "text": "The meaning of the assumption is that without switching, the design problem to obtain an optimal controller in K m can be transformed into a convex program and solved completely. Most centralized design problems and some design problems in decentralized control fit here; for example, see [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] .",
